[SN]TITLE[SN]
Grammys 2017: Winners and Nominees

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Adele was the big winner at the 2017 Grammys, taking home five trophies.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Amongst her haul were three of the "big four" awards: Song of the year, record of the year and album of the year.
The last time someone achieved that was in 2012. And it was Adele.
Here's a list of the winners and nominees in the main categories. You can see the complete list of 84 categories on the official Grammys website.
